videos.headline: Ragas rushes 31 yards for TD
videos.description: Trey Ragas breaks through the pile to burst for a 31-yard touchdown to pad the Ragin' Cajuns' lead over the Aggies.

videos.headline: Davis goes deep for TD
videos.description: Jordan Davis connects with Ryheem Malone for a 33-yard touchdown to give the Ragin' Cajuns the lead.
